{"title":"邓拓逝世二十周年","authors":["左漠野"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":5,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓拓逝世二十周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左漠野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少小寒窗不等闲，从戎抗敌雁门关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如钢党性垂功业，似水雄文出马鞍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片丹心存夜话，千秋明月照燕山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书生冷对焚坑事，公道人心两样看。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}